item.title: CVE-2018-18994|2024-08-05T11:23:08.915Z -- lcds%20laquis -- lcds%20laquis%20scada
item.description: LCDS Laquis SCADA prior to version 4.1.0.4150 allows an out of bounds read when opening a specially crafted project file, which may cause a system crash or allow data exfiltration.
